                            <h3>    <a href="/article/independent-halves-annual-losses-46m/1353976" data-url="https://www.campaignlive.co.uk/article/independent-halves-annual-losses-46m/1353976" data-id="1353976" title="The Independent halves annual losses to &#163;4.6m">The Independent halves annual losses to &#163;4.6m</a>
</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="storyContent">
                            <div class="mediaWrapper">
